OL,5, Three rugby union clubs in England are 
OL,6, to begin trialling scanning technology 
OL,7, to monitor players' brain health.      
OL,9,FResearchers hope a device which        
OL,10,Fmeasures brain patterns could help     
OL,11,Fmedical personnel spot and manage      
OL,12,Fconcussion, and make sports safer.     
OL,14,FThe work is still in its infancy, but  
OL,15,Fthe idea is to get a baseline scan to  
OL,16,Fuse for comparison if an injury occurs.
OL,18,FIt is one of a number of projects aimed
OL,19,Fat improving how contact sports deal   
OL,20,Fwith concussion risk.                  
